title: DOMINION OCE
body: Why is there no dominion on OCE i know alot of people that would play in the weekends, atleast a couple of trial weekends should happen to test it

replies.body: You bring more Summoners to this game and riot will bring out dominion. (mabye)

We don't even have Normal Draft what makes you think we'll be getting Dominion anytime soon. We recently just got 24 ranked queues and even that was a trial period. Slow down, how long has OCE been up? We simply don't have the playerbase for it yet, and as mentioned it's not even that popular on NA. Before OCE, I rarely played Dominion and when I did, the queues took a solid 5-10 minutes.
I doubt they will, Dominion isn't even popular in NA. They'll retire it soon I imagine for a practice mode (not sandbox) or something similar.
